{"tid":1695242,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"8月5號罷工最成功既行業就係機場","createTime":"2019-11-05T13:51:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T16:41:05.000Z","uid":81236,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6cd0e129ac8331f0e4e28777383029b5225f77b9","tid":1695242,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T13:51:28.000Z","msg":"除左因為有堵路塞鐵配合<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最主要就係因為機場有工會</span></span><br />\n<br />\n要大罷工唔係日日問點解啲人仲唔肯罷工<br />\n<br />\n唔係今日話要聽日罷工<br />\n<br />\n唔係話下星期要罷一星期工<br />\n<br />\n罷工問題唔係在於幾時罷工<br />\n<br />\n有幾多個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />話肯罷工<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">而係點樣組織罷工</span></span><br />\n<br />\n罷工唔係得個講字，係做要<br />\n<br />\n點做？<br />\n<br />\n就係要搵志同道合既人一齊組織工會<br />\n<br />\n為左你自己同埋同事利益著想<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>組織工會啦</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"9b8e0a140986a677154a62ef490140cd5b41cef0","tid":1695242,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T13:53:00.000Z","msg":"公務員工會上線了<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1693993\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1693993</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bc2ecc1fa82e03a4920c7e2ab195de641f855755","tid":1695242,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T13:53:37.000Z","msg":"［突發］ 國泰工會罷工<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1202628\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1202628</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"890b293c9a16f25969c741cfe5d12c6fd9fa1119","tid":1695242,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T13:54:18.000Z","msg":"工會係罷工嘅必要條件"},{"pid":"b0ea461d934d4fe7f7a88395aa46ca8dbf2e73c1","tid":1695242,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T13:56:08.000Z","msg":"我宣布三罷籌備工作正式開始<br />\n